nded by crowds at airports or been the subject of vicious arguments online between rival fan camps, leading Chinese official media to denounce fans for being \\\"visibly aggressive\\\".\", \"from\": 877, \"to\": 1084, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1013, \"end\": 1020, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"score\": 0.9999927747814576, \"rank\": 4.537262614054293e-06, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"E-paper  Newsletters  Podcasts  RSS Feed  About Us  Terms & Conditions  Privacy Policy  Need help?\", \"from\": 1086, \"to\": 1184, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1118, \"end\": 1126, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RSS\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"RSS Feed\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RSS\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RSS\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Reach us here.\", \"from\": 1185, \"to\": 1199, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Advertise with us\", \"from\": 1201, \"to\": 1218, \"entities\": []}]}"